<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qcameraselector.xml">Qt3DRender::QCameraSelector</db:link> can be used to select the camera, which is used by the FrameGraph when drawing the entities.</db:para>
</db:section>
